title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show OCT-24-2013 THURS
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show OCT-24-2013 THURS






The Glenn Beck Program




                
      
      The Glenn Beck Program - 10/24/13Thursday, October 24, 2013 10:45 AM




The Glenn Beck Program is Live Monday - Friday from 9am - 12pm ET




More ridiculousness in congress as the GOP are called terrorists 
  and the Democrats are called reasonable,
   and Glenn calls for all Americans to #DefundtheGOP.

  Also, CBS shows that healthcare.gov doesn't estimate accurately.

  Plus, Glen recalls his daughter's recent experience giving birth 
    and how she was treated,

     giving a perfect example of how one employee can ruin an entire company,

        and that this is the future of universal healthcare.

  And, the police state is rapidly encroaching on American's freedoms.
